<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">

    <h2>Hello {{ OwnerName }},</h2>

    <p>
        Congratulations!
    </p>

    <p>
        Your restaurant
        <strong>{{ RestaurantName }}</strong>
        has been approved by the FoodRush team.
    </p>

    <p>
        You can now continue the onboarding process, complete your restaurant setup,
        and start receiving customer orders.
    </p>

    <p>
        Thank you for choosing <strong>FoodRush</strong>.
    </p>

    <p>
        Best regards,<br />
        <strong>FoodRush Team</strong>
    </p>

</body>

</html>